Portions ported from Actual Budget
(https://github.com/actualbudget/actual)

The CRDT sync engine in `Actuali/Actuali/Services/Sync/` (including the
hybrid logical clock, Merkle tree, MurmurHash3, sync protobuf schema, and
CRDT message semantics) is a Swift port of code from the Actual Budget
project (`packages/crdt` and `packages/loot-core`), which is distributed
under the MIT license:

Copyright James Long

